                <h1>Where Bill Gates Grew Up: His Seattle Roots</h1>
                <p>Bill Gates grew up in Seattle, Washington, where he was born on October 28, 1955. From a young age, he displayed exceptional intellect and a keen interest in computers. Raised in an upper-middle-class family, Gates attended Lakeside School, where he first encountered programming on a computer. His early experiences laid the foundation for his later success.</p>
